is it a trend for people to be attached??
cant people just be single?it tends to get lonely at times..
but look on the bright side...u get alot of time to do ur own things n u dont need to report to anyone.
y is it that some ppl r so proud of their bfs or gfs n some r not?
my mind is currently filled with these type of question..
relationships...can we live with it?can we live without it??

its gonna be short today..im dead tired..n im having gastric again..i need to watch tv or something to calm down..today i didnt go to college again..cos i was having headache when i woke up..went to my sisters office to eat lunch n went there to BS with her collegues...n talk....n talk....went to my sisters house for dinner cos today is "tong yuen" celebration...her mother in law cooked alot of things..ive no mood to write anything today..cos JEONSA called me a bitch today..he say i sit in my small room n bitch n moan everyday..i guess he doesnt understand wats the feeling like,stayin in a small room eveeryday when u have no one to talk to abt ur problems...no one to complain to...all i can say is..F^%& u!u dont know wat ive been thru through out the past 1 1/2 years..u dont know how difficult it has been for me..i know wat its like to stay with crazy ppl n wat its like to sleep on the streets...........

not gonna write anything today..having headache..i slept at 3 yday,doin work for todays presentation...d is ignoring me..cos he say hes busy typing letters for his dads new company..i wonder if its true..see u tom..

yday nite,i talked ot ivy before i went to sleep....we were talkin abt alot of things...she asked abt d but we ended up talkin abt something else...suddenly she asked abt my friends..the bunch of friends who used to be my close friends...who decided to ignore me now..she asked me y we turned up this way..she said there must be a misunderstanding..i dunno it aws happens to me..friends leave me..but some do remain..i guess these ppl n me were never meant to be...
today i woke up n went to my sisters house to make cookies for christmas..it was fun..i wish i could bake things too..im sick of moving around..i  wish i have a place i could stay for long..ate dinner at my sisters house...as usual..very full cos her mother in law likes to cook alot...she likes the table filled with food..feel very fulll..the day pass by so fast today..at least im not bored like the usual me..im gonna take a shower now n start wrapping christmas gifts..

today is the first day im on the net since wednesday..the stupid buggers at tmnet jus suddenly decided to suspend my account because i havent paid my bills yet..it is jus plain stupid cos i didnt recieve any warning,whatsoever..
i went bead shopping again today..the people at the shop now recognise me n ms n mrs low..haha..mrs low is my sis carine n ms low is joanne,her sis in law..went to get some stuff for the chain for spectacles cos i jus realise last night that i dont know how to end the chain..asked the people at the shop to teach me..then after that went to petaling street to eat..i was scared cos the place was dirty n there was alot of ppl n beggars..im scared of these 3 things: beggars,dirty n smelly places n a place that is so crowded that ppl bump into u.the food was good n cheap.. =) yummy..
yday nite i went to mid valley to buy some stuff...guess wat?a fight nearly broke out in front of mid valley..3 guys frm 3 cars came out of their car n scolded this dude in a pajero..a girl came out of the pajero n started shouting "stop it..go away" hahaah it aused a massive jam cos everyone was bein a typical malaysian..driving slow to look =p 
i think im goin to 1 utama later,i wanan go to la senza n buy something ;) chritmas underwear..christmas is my fav time of the year..cos the decoration is nice..n christmas music is nice too =) i suddenly thought of goin to starbucks..but i got no one to go with..so boring!!ahh!but nonetheless...still in the creative mood

it has been ages since the last time i updated my journal..i tried updating this stupid thing 3 times today..this is the 3rd time im updating it..i was talking to david about online journals n decided to update this journal ..at least i have somewhere to voice my views..ive deleted all my old entries..cos its a new beginning =) we shall start all over again!
well..lemme explain y i havent been updating this thing..ive been busy with college..alot of work..3 subjects cram into 3 mths..i think i must have made the wrong choice joinin this stupid CSU shit..other than that..have been busy travelling frm house no 1 to house no 3(house no 1 is kl,house no 2 is my parents house in my hometown,house no 3 is singapore) i sound like a nomad dont i?well..at a point i was really travellin alot...i went to singapore like once a mth..so every mth very broke but very happy =) cos i get to see D..we argue alot cos we dont see each other alot..but other than that,we were happy =) esp when we were together..but now..i dunno wats happening to us..im confused..i dont know if we r together or not..
other things that happened recently..my sis got married...my parents moved into a new house..which means i ahave my own room now =) im still thinkin how im gonna decorate it..umm..n ive also been busy makin my own ear rings n bracelets n all that..as christmas presents for ppl..ill get someone to take the pics n post them here
